23template <typename T>
24class Nullable final
25{
26 bool m_hasValue = false;
27 T m_value;
28
29public:
30 Nullable() = default;
31 Nullable(const T &value) : m_hasValue(true), m_value(value) {}
32 Nullable(T &&value) : m_hasValue(true), m_value(std::move(value)) {}
33 Nullable(std::nullptr_t) {}
34
35 Nullable<T> & operator=(const T &value) {
36 m_hasValue = true;
37 m_value = value;
38 return *this;
39 }
40
41 Nullable<T> & operator=(T &&value) {
42 m_hasValue = true;
43 m_value = std::move(value);
44 return *this;
45 }
46
47 Nullable<T> & operator=(std::nullptr_t) {
48 m_hasValue = false;
49 m_value = T();
50 return *this;
51 }
52
53 operator T() const {
54 if (!m_hasValue) {
55 throw std::logic_error("Access empty value");
56 }
57 return m_value;
58 }
59
60 bool hasValue() const {
61 return m_hasValue;
62 }
63
64 const T & value() const {
65 return m_value;
66 }
67
68 T & value() {
69 return m_value;
70 }
71
72 friend inline bool operator==(const Nullable &a, const Nullable &b) {
73 return a.m_hasValue == b.m_hasValue && (!a.m_hasValue || a.m_value == b.m_value);
74 }
75 friend inline bool operator!=(const Nullable &a, const Nullable &b) {
76 return !(a == b);
77 }
78
79 friend inline bool operator==(const Nullable &a, const T &v) {
80 return a.m_hasValue && a.m_value == v;
81 }
82 friend inline bool operator!=(const Nullable &a, const T &v) {
83 return !(a == v);
84 }
85
86 friend inline bool operator==(const T &v, const Nullable &a) {
87 return a.m_hasValue && a.m_value == v;
88 }
89 friend inline bool operator!=(const T &v, const Nullable &a) {
90 return !(v == a);
91 }
92
93 friend inline bool operator==(const Nullable &a, std::nullptr_t) {
94 return !a.m_hasValue;
95 }
96 friend inline bool operator!=(const Nullable &a, std::nullptr_t) {
97 return a.m_hasValue;
98 }
99
100 friend inline bool operator==(std::nullptr_t, const Nullable &a) {
101 return !a.m_hasValue;
102 }
103 friend inline bool operator!=(std::nullptr_t, const Nullable &a) {
104 return a.m_hasValue;
105 }
106
107 friend inline void swap(Nullable &a, Nullable &b) {
108 using std::swap;
109 swap(a.m_value, b.m_value);
110 swap(a.m_hasValue, b.m_hasValue);
111 }
112};
